                <</type>>
              <</replace>>
            <</link>><<print "\n">>

            <<link "→ 下令处死地狱犬">>
              <<replace "#selection">>
                <<type 40ms skipkey " " >>
                  什么东西？胡言乱语！处死！<<print "\n">>
