                    <<type 40ms skipkey " " >>
                      <<bookflipgoto "第一页">>公爵大人离开了诊所。<</bookflipgoto>><<print "\n">>
                      <<set $time += 1>>
                    <</type>>
                  <</replace>>
                <</link>><<print "\n">>
                <<bookflipgoto "诊所">>→ 还有别的事<</bookflipgoto>>
              </div>

